 3. Architecture Overview
3.1 Medallion Architecture
The Medallion Architecture organises data into four progressively refined layers. Each layer has a distinct purpose, quality contract, and write strategy.

Layer	Container	Format	Purpose	Write Mode
Raw	raw/	JSON (day-partitioned)	Landing zone — exact copy of source data, no transformation	Append only — never modified
Bronze	bronze/	Delta Lake	Raw ingestion with audit lineage columns — all types as String	Append (Auto Loader stream)
Silver	silver/	Delta Lake	Cleaned, type-cast, anomaly-fixed — production-quality data	MERGE (upsert by primary key)
Gold	gold/	Delta Lake (Unity Catalog managed)	Pre-aggregated KPIs for Power BI — one table per audience	Full overwrite per run

