 4. Synthetic Data Generation
4.1 Why Synthetic Data
This project uses entirely synthetic data for two reasons: (1) no real pet owner or device data exists in a portfolio context, and (2) synthetic data allows precise control over data distributions, anomaly rates, referential integrity, and scenario coverage without privacy concerns. All 14 tables were generated using Python scripts with realistic business rules and sensor simulation.

